{"content":"    \n   <div class=\"DashboardScreen \"   id=\"DashboardScreen\" savrWidType=\"SCREEN\" >\n               <div class=\"DashboardScreen_Dashboard\" savrWidType=\"RECT\" \n         >\n        \n                 <div class=\"DashboardScreen_Dashboard_txt\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Dashboard\n        \n      </div>\n      \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"DashboardScreen_Stats_row\"    savrWidType=\"ROW\" >\n          <div class=\"savrintersub_DashboardScreen_Stats_row\" style=\"    display: flex; width: max-content; \n      gap: 2px 10px;\n    justify-content: flex-start;\n        align-items: center;\n    \">\n                     <div class=\"indicard_3\" savrWidType=\"RECT\" \n         >\n        \n                 <div class=\"img_3\"   savrWidType=\"IMAGE\"  >\n             \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"title_3\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        +20%\n        \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"subtitle_3\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Stat 1 desc...\n        \n      </div>\n      \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"indicard_4\" savrWidType=\"RECT\" \n         >\n        \n                 <div class=\"img_4\"   savrWidType=\"IMAGE\"  >\n             \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"title_4\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        +50%\n        \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"subtitle_4\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Stat 2 desc...\n        \n      </div>\n      \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"indicard_5\" savrWidType=\"RECT\" \n         >\n        \n                 <div class=\"img_5\"   savrWidType=\"IMAGE\"  >\n             \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"title_5\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        +70%\n        \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"subtitle_5\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Stat 3 desc...\n        \n      </div>\n      \n      </div>\n      \n          </div>\n        </div>\n               <div class=\"indicard_6\" savrWidType=\"RECT\" \n         >\n        \n                 <div class=\"title_6\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Graph stats\n        \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"stat\" savrWidType=\"STAT\" \n         >\n        \n        \n      </div>\n      \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"txt_Das\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Orders\n        \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"DashboardScreen_Trades\" savrWidType=\"grid_column\" \n          \n          >\n        \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"DashboardScreen_nav\" savrWidType=\"RECT\" \n         >\n        \n                 <div class=\"nav_Dashboard\"   savrWidType=\"IMAGE\"  >\n             \n      </div>\n               <div class=\"DashboardScreen_Dashboard_txt_1\" savrWidType=\"TEXT\" \n         >\n        Dashboard\n        \n      </div>\n      \n      </div>\n      \n  </div>\n    ","code":"import traceback\nasync def run_main_savr():\n    try:\n        import ginni as g\n        \n        async def initialize_dashboard():\n            # Set Toolbar and Section Titles\n            g.GinNode('DashboardScreen_Dashboard_txt').set_text_context('Financial Dashboard')\n            g.GinNode('txt_Das').set_text_context('Recent Transactions')\n            g.GinNode('title_6').set_text_context('Expense Distribution')\n        \n            # Render Realistic Financial Chart\n            # Showing a breakdown of monthly expenses\n            expense_data = {\n                'Rent': 2500,\n                'Payroll': 8000,\n                'Software': 450,\n                'Marketing': 1200,\n                'Utilities': 300\n            }\n            graph_stat = g.GinNode('stat')\n            graph_stat.render_chart(expense_data, 'pie', chartName='Monthly Expenses')\n        \n            # Populate Transactions Adapter with realistic data\n            transactions = [\n                {'title': 'Stripe Payout', 'subtitle': '+$4,250.00 • Completed'},\n                {'title': 'Amazon Web Services', 'subtitle': '-$142.50 • Processing'},\n                {'title': 'Office Rent', 'subtitle': '-$2,500.00 • Completed'},\n                {'title': 'Apple Inc. Service', 'subtitle': '-$9.99 • Completed'},\n                {'title': 'Client Payment: Acme Corp', 'subtitle': '+$1,800.00 • Completed'},\n                {'title': 'Starbucks Coffee', 'subtitle': '-$5.75 • Completed'}\n            ]\n        \n            mytemplate_id = 'indicard_7'\n            adapter_id = 'DashboardScreen_Trades'\n            \n            for tx in transactions:\n                list_item = await g.create_widget_type(template_id=mytemplate_id, parent_id=adapter_id)\n                list_item.get_child('title_7').set_text_context(tx['title'])\n                list_item.get_child('subtitle_6').set_text_context(tx['subtitle'])\n        \n            # Setup Navigation\n            nav_btn = g.GinNode('nav_Dashboard')\n            nav_txt = g.GinNode('DashboardScreen_Dashboard_txt_1')\n            \n            async def navigate_home(e):\n                g.moveto('DashboardScreen')\n                g.show_toast('Already on Dashboard')\n        \n            nav_btn.set_on_click(navigate_home)\n            nav_txt.set_on_click(navigate_home)\n        \n        # Execute initialization\n        import asyncio\n        asyncio.create_task(initialize_dashboard())\n        pgst = g.GinNode('top-progress')\n        pgst.set_visibility(False)\n        g.print('ginniPageLoadMarker8900883612800000')\n    except Exception:\n       consolelogerror(traceback.format_exc())\n\nimport asyncio\nloop = asyncio.get_event_loop()\nresult = loop.run_until_complete(run_main_savr())\n       ","css":"          .DashboardScreen { background: rgba(248, 250, 252, 1); height: 100dvh; width: 100vw;  display:inline-block;overflow-y: scroll;overflow-x: hidden; flex: 0 0 auto;position: relative;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;} \n .DashboardScreen_Dashboard { background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); height: 30px; width: 100%; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;position: absolute;  top: 6px;} \n .DashboardScreen_Dashboard_txt {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-color: transparent; border: none; resize: none; color: rgba(255, 94, 0, 1); height: 30px; width: 120px; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  font-weight: 700;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;overflow-y: hidden;overflow-x: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;position: absolute;  top: 6px;  left: 36px;} \n .DashboardScreen_Stats_row { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1); height: 108px; width: 100%; text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; white-space: nowrap;overflow-x: scroll;background: transparent; gap: 30px;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;position: absolute;  top: 51px;} \n .indicard_3 { background: rgba(248, 250, 252, 1); height: 90px; width: 180px; box-shadow: 0px 2px 4px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto; flex: 0 0 auto;position: relative;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 6px 6px 6px 6px;} \n .img_3 { background: rgba(255, 94, 0, 1); height: 72px; width: 72px; box-shadow: none; object-fit: cover; filter: invert(29%) sepia(100%) saturate(5.98) brightness(1.32) contrast(1.78); background-color: transparent; background-image: url('images/placeholders/Stats.png'); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;position: absolute;  top: calc(50% + -39px);  left: 6px;} \n .title_3 {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-color: transparent; border: none; resize: none; color: rgba(28, 28, 30, 1); height: 36px; width: 105px; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 18px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  font-weight: 800;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;overflow-y: hidden;overflow-x: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;position: absolute;  top: 6px;  left: 81px;} \n .subtitle_3 {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-color: transparent; border: none; resize: none; color: rgba(28, 28, 30, 0.5882352941176471); height: 36px; width: 99px; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  font-weight: 400;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;position: absolute;  top: 33px;  left: 81px;} \n .indicard_4 { background: rgba(248, 250, 252, 1); height: 90px; width: 180px; box-shadow: 0px 2px 4px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto; flex: 0 0 auto;position: relative;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 6px 6px 6px 6px;} \n .img_4 { background: rgba(255, 94, 0, 0.5882352941176471); height: 72px; width: 72px; box-shadow: none; object-fit: cover; filter: invert(28%) sepia(96%) saturate(4.49) hue-rotate(340deg) brightness(1.42) contrast(1.40); background-color: transparent; background-image: url('images/placeholders/Stats.png'); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;position: absolute;  top: calc(50% + -39px);  left: 6px;} \n .title_4 {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-color: transparent; border: none; resize: none; color: rgba(28, 28, 30, 1); height: 36px; width: 105px; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 18px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  font-weight: 800;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;overflow-y: hidden;overflow-x: hidden; white-space: nowrap; text-overflow: ellipsis;position: absolute;  top: 6px;  left: 81px;} \n .subtitle_4 {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-color: transparent; border: none; resize: none; color: rgba(28, 28, 30, 0.5882352941176471); height: 36px; width: 99px; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  font-weight: 400;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;position: absolute;  top: 33px;  left: 81px;} \n .indicard_5 { background: rgba(248, 250, 252, 1); height: 90px; width: 180px; box-shadow: 0px 2px 4px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.07); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto; flex: 0 0 auto;position: relative;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 6px 6px 6px 6px;} \n .img_5 { background: rgba(255, 94, 0, 0.19607843137254902); height: 72px; width: 72px; box-shadow: none; object-fit: cover; filter: invert(26%) sepia(91%) saturate(4.42) hue-rotate(340deg) brightness(1.56) contrast(1.62); background-color: transparent; background-image: url('images/placeholders/Stats.png'); text-align: start; font-size: 12px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;border:0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);border-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;position: absolute;  top: calc(50% + -39px);  left: 6px;} \n .title_5 {white-space: normal;\n  word-wrap: break-word;\n  overflow-wrap: break-word; background: transparent; background-color: transparent; border: none; resize: none; color: rgba(28, 28, 30, 1); height: 36px; width: 105px; box-shadow: none; text-align: start; font-size: 18px; background-size:  cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: center center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px;  font-weight: 800;  display:inline-block;overflow: auto;overflow-y: hidden;overf